    "description": "<p><strong>AUDIMARS BUILDTECH PTE LTD </strong>was founded in 2011 by Mr Soo Chee Wai. Since then, the company has established a growing reputation for excellence in quality and delivery in the building industry.</p>\n<p><strong>AUDIMARS BUILDTECH PTE LTD</strong> started off in 2011 as a building and civil engineering firm carrying out sub-contracting work for mainly contractors such as JJ &amp; TH Holdings , Expand Construction. During these initial years, we successfully completed some prestigious projects including erection joss paper burner(Client Kong Meng San Phor Kark See), retrofitting work to existing suspended ceiling, Architecture wet work, erection of 5th Block of Apartment.</p>",
